Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNINC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.47,0:00:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的方式驕傲地去面對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNINC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"機動戰艦"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.84,0:00:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍著痛苦所踢起的小石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若反彈回來也會變成鑽石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上到手的夢想不算是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是請堅信它一定會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.76,0:01:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡從不氣餒的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.10,0:01:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有想哭的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會永遠永遠在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNINC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的方式驕傲地去面對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去熱衷的日子是夢的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNINC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那碎片收集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能看見以明天為目標的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO BE...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOING YOUR DAY'S GROW UP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻色子，費米子變換開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS可以了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耐壓AESTI降下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力場擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測出大量光子，重力子，中子增大中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTI的螢幕順利運作中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上接觸跳躍力場了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探測器運作開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探測器沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備進入磁場 要進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生體玻色子跳躍的實驗全都失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子從火星到出現在月球軌道上花了半年多...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,番紅花也跑到在地球上被消滅之前的火星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻色子跳躍和瞬間移動是不一樣的現象也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"CC"是玻色子跳躍的關鍵這假設已因此被否定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據我在撫子收集的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生體玻色子跳躍的可能性還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓NERGAL有損失的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把握這個機會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"真實"不是只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被邀請去赤月的房間好興奮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿什麼衣服去呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來以為戰艦跟聖誕節無緣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊，聖誕節
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，能搭上撫子真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，別停下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不認真工作的話是無法參加晚上的宴會喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家參加宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起渡過美妙的一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主將降臨到你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱著花束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著香檳，主將降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論地球或火星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:04:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MERRY CHRISTMAS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:04:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美妙的夢將到來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，嗯，漂亮漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像有點歪耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NERGAL重工協辦 聖誕舞會?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶而鬧一下也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是一直都在鬧嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我們已經受邀參加赤月的舞會了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，這邊的來賓是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來賓?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出席者啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MERRY CHRISTMAS今夜是祭典唷...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠，妳也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我PASS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟聖誕節還是該和喜歡的人一起渡過才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一份鍋燒烏龍麵...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無關什麼喜歡或不喜歡...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情，對，因為友情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，我也PASS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河你在哪兒，天河
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦，天河跑到哪兒去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:05:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MERRY CHRISTMAS無論誰都會來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來也好，那種玩意兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不問人方不方便就擅自決定…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河 你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙鋼人出動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回，最終回"大決戰，永遠的激鋼人"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一集啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然到三十八集為止我已經看過好幾次了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這一集一直沒看過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊，這豪華的會場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級愛情攻勢遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢特製連連看機器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，少女們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是大家都說要去參加赤月的宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑開得太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，沒有人會來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶而在這種地方也不錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我離開撫子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是到總公司上班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不會是討厭跟我在同一個工作場所吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子會變得更危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也很危險啊 到處都是餓狼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成員將會被正式徵召
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候要退出也不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，也就是說這是聖誕禮物嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反對，反對...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"橫須賀港地球連合宇宙戰艦船塢"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直讓民間人來當軍艦的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來全員都要捲鋪蓋的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我破例...為了我的撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜託上級將各位編入軍旅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰拜託你了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人痛心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算過上次因為思兼失控給地球聯合軍帶來的損失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看來不只是付不出各位的薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許還不得不反過來要求賠償吶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩周前在月球的軍方勢力下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了不明的大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此也考慮過把撫子編入月球方面軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算離開撫子也得接受令人不快的監視
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何，請你們體諒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，你要怎樣啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得把戰爭當成工作有點怪怪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊…你不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒道理老是把AESTI交給外行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次補充了優秀的飛行員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明人要專職當廚師了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據我們的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在迪尼西安島和竹節蟲時擅自行動…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為你缺乏當軍人的資質
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後希望你以民間人的身份好好做為軍方的後盾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要接受監視
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要我離開撫子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是這裡不是屬於你的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了，天河
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是等到我們打敗木星蜥蜴的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定能夠以笑容再見的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想嘗嘗你的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也退出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MERRY CHRISTMAS今夜是祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一晚就要好好狂歡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的上帝...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家說我是多餘的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且當軍人就是命令下來叫你做什麼就做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去商量看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你要棄摯愛的我於不顧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不愛妳呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不愛妳呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香，這段時間打擾妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，走吧，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒說完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像新婚夫妻...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠，今後打算怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當廚師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是又會被人說是不成材的飛行員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使說出我想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕也沒人願意雇我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們邀你過去，不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這麼說其實是想監視明人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:09:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份工作只有你才能做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我能?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星蜥蜴靠鬱金香做一種瞬間移動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是進行玻色子跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行幾乎無止盡的攻擊你們也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NERGAL和地球軍分別
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急於解析這個系統
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星蜥蜴自始就是無人兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而番紅花也全軍覆沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有撫子能夠讓生物活著進行玻色子跳躍呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個原因就在天河身土
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮斯小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她對我們的實驗有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人想要實現生體玻色子跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能將載人兵器送去火星或木星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰況也會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟地球沒有木星那樣優良的無人兵器製造技術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，木星在生體玻色子跳躍上也沒有成功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他們得到這技術之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須搶先才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的確擁有不可思議的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球需要它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是明人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人只是個普通的飛行員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是CC
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然稱為鬱金香水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是在火星發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看過這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在火星遺失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CC最初是在火星極冠的礦山被發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就由NERGAL全權管理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是CC
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是CC，怎樣，很驚訝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多，怎麼會有這麼多?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，天河你的CC怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些水晶和鬱金香的組成是同樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的假設是…CC是玻色子跳躍的引信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天你從火星飛來地球不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從火星飛來地球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來的時候已經在地球上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜子上的石頭也不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣，請你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和伊妮斯珍貴的資料對人類的未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉娜小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經做過活體實驗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，因為無聊就跟來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離實驗成功還很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，那只是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟伊妮斯只是白老鼠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太骯髒了，NEGCAL...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當白老鼠有什麼關係?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你只是半吊子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了人類，有什麼關係?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當白老鼠還比較了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這話也太...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定沒問題，會成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫助我們，好不好?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不留住他嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙這樣下去才真正是半吊子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看上他了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在胡說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說要趕在木星蜥蜴之前\N得到活體玻色子跳躍的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說他們和我們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是在某處得到相轉移引擎和鬱金香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防壁裝置遭到破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從鬱金香內部有強烈的次元歪曲防壁產生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測出大量的包斯粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果實驗機已經到達敵方的母星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被發現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球方面的活體玻色子跳躍實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話，他們會想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨礙實驗…然後破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向梅麗小姐和克利少爺道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅麗，克利，抱歉了\N(音同MERRY CHRISTMAS)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"赤月緊急參加"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…媽媽，買車子給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻孩子 我們欠人家的債有一火車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續待在那個公司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我會窒息的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川崎市有木星蜥蜴出現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂，今夜是祭典...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼，激鋼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合軍全滅了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然敵人只是小規模的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有重力波炮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為免妨礙戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託請勿在川崎地區開車和去看熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外，目前木星蜥蜴...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是答應要忘記撫子跟我過聖誕節嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想打仗嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我在火星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是就這樣失去撫子的話我就沒有能守護的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能守護我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看起來很快樂 看起來很悠閒嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實，大家都在拚命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在自己的立場上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了守護自己的幸福而拚命地戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是因為戰爭才了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為保護一個女孩子而生和為保護地球而生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一樣是戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力場算什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一記
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼，怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上前去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要抓住它再怎麼瞬間移動也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一那是玻色子跳躍的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活人不就...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新來的，喂，新來的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了，不在座艙裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中攻擊剩下的一架
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三秒後，右三十度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看出跳躍的模式就能贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初就設定成自爆用的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自爆?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要對周圍的空間全體進行相轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來可保證讓這城市消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真糟…可是應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人君?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把CC給我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我才能做的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做些什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最後的最後當個戰士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人不是這麼單純的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是妳…都是妳害了明人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別激動 要找天河君的話…妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，撫子…撫子...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於接通了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼搞的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩星期哦!明明兩星期來都在呼叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他飛走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到兩星期前的月球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:19:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香…妳在哭嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼，真的是你?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也搞不太清楚…在月球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了，我馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，妳想來就來啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人最喜歡我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想呼喚著明日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰在唱激鋼人的歌?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是，從這裏面傳來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧，這是無人兵器啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的感動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:21:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有純粹的情感沈睡其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要追尋夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容與淚水的數目就會漸漸增多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時想要更像自我地去感受風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不屬於其他人的我自己的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去發掘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀，各位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是GEKIGER JET的駕駛員 天空劍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗黑環帶宇宙的阿卡拉王子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送來了恐怖的機械怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打倒這個的只有激鋼爆炎了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，次回的激鋼人3特別篇你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對，次回 本節目由美人新艦長御統百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不對!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回機動戰艦撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"像熱血卡通般去吧"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.67,0:22:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S GEKIGER IN!


